Interface ApplicationEntity

All Superinterfaces:
SystemEntity, SystemObject, TransferableObject
All Known Subinterfaces:

All Known Implementing Classes:
AbstractApplicationEntity, CustomCodeMetadata, CustomLibMetadata, DataSourceMetadata, DBObjectMetadata, EntityMetadata, FilterMetadata, FormMetadata, MenuMetadata, ReportMetadata, RestMetadata, TaskMetadata, TransferMetadata, TransformerMetadata, UserGroupMetadata
public interface ApplicationEntity extends SystemEntity, TransferableObject
An ApplicationEntity represents a SystemEntity, that is transferable and can be part of a module. It also supports a permission management to restrict access.
Author:
seed-master
